Bamsurgeon: tools for adding mutations to .bam files, used for testing mutation callers

Please see doc/Manual.pdf for instructions and contact ewingad@soe.ucsc.edu with questions.

Prerequisites:

samtools/wgsim/tabix (http://samtools.sourceforge.net/)
pysam (http://code.google.com/p/pysam/)
bwa (http://bio-bwa.sourceforge.net/)
velvet (http://www.ebi.ac.uk/~zerbino/velvet/)
